<p><a name="Update_on_democides" id="Update_on_democides"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Democide&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4" title="Edit section: Update on democides">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Update on democides</span></h2>
<p>In May 2005, Rummel guessed the number for <a href="/wiki/Darfur_Conflict" title="Darfur Conflict" class="mw-redirect">Darfur Conflict</a> to be <a href="http://freedomspeace.blogspot.com/2005/05/democide-galore_08.html" class="external text" title="http://freedomspeace.blogspot.com/2005/05/democide-galore_08.html" rel="nofollow">over 400,000.</a></p>
<p>In November 2005, he estimated the alleged democide in <a href="/wiki/Mao_Zedong" title="Mao Zedong">Mao</a>'s <a href="/wiki/People%27s_Republic_of_China" title="People's Republic of China">China</a> (1949–1975) at 73,000,000.<sup id="cite_ref-reeval_Mao_9-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-reeval_Mao-9" title=""><span>[</span>10<span>]</span></a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-reeval_Mao_2_10-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-reeval_Mao_2-10" title=""><span>[</span>11<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
<p>In December 2005, he raised his estimate for colonial democide to 50,000,000 and estimated the democide in the <a href="/wiki/Congo_Free_State" title="Congo Free State">Congo Free State</a> to 10,000,000.<sup id="cite_ref-Colonial_11-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Colonial-11" title=""><span>[</span>12<span>]</span></a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-20th_12-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-20th-12" title=""><span>[</span>13<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
<p><a name="See_also" id="See_also"></a></p>
